{"word":"G3648 - ὁλόκληρος - holóklēros - hol'-ok'-lay-ros - Entire","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁλόκληρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">holóklēros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hol'-ok'-lay-ros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Entire</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"முழுவதுமான, நிறைவுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"complete in all its parts, in no part lacking or unsound, complete, entire, whole"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3650 - ὅλος - hólos - hol'-os/3650\">G3650</a> and <a href=\"#/G2819 - κλῆρος - klēros - klay'-ros/2819\">G2819</a>; <i>complete</i> in every <i>part</i>, that is, perfectly <i>sound</i> (in body): - entire, whole.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2624/2624\">G2624</a>, <a href=\"#/G2816/2816\">G2816</a>, <a href=\"#/G2817/2817\">G2817</a>, <a href=\"#/G2818/2818\">G2818</a>, <a href=\"#/G2819/2819\">G2819</a>, <a href=\"#/G2820/2820\">G2820</a>, <a href=\"#/G3647/3647\">G3647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3648/3648\">G3648</a>, <a href=\"#/G4345/4345\">G4345</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789/4789\">G4789</a>"}]}